review 1:
Simple meaty restaurant with nice rice paddy view.
Their cooking way is really good, I'm addicted with their French fries. Also there is concept without MSG!!!
I ordered pork ribs. Humble price, nice size and good amount of fat.
They have es jeruk which have rich taste.
If you come to nearby, just drop in for a rest!! You'll have good chilling experience with lovely food and view there!!
review 2: beautiful place overlooking a rice field. delicious cuisine. I'll be back!
review 3:
We ordered Tuna Pizza, Vanabi Fried Rice, Mushroom Tempe Soup, Nasi Campur, Orange Juice, and Mango Juice. Every food is tasty.

The atmosphere on thursday lunch time is very calm & relaxing. Definitely will come back here next time.
